<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Pagina no encontrada</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg-top: #eef6ff;
    --bg-bottom: #dcecff;
    --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
    --text: #16324f;
    --muted: #5f748d;
    --accent: #0b84f3;
    --accent-dark: #0868bf;
    --shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(17, 44, 77, 0.18);
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px;
    font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    color: var(--text);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(11, 132, 243, 0.18), transparent 32%),
      radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.12), transparent 28%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-top), var(--bg-bottom));
  }

  .error-shell {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1080px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    border-radius: 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }

  .error-copy {
    padding: 56px;
  }

  .error-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(11, 132, 243, 0.1);
    color: var(--accent-dark);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .error-copy h1 {
    margin: 18px 0 14px;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.4rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
  }

  .error-copy p {
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    max-width: 520px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .error-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 220px;
    padding: 15px 24px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #39a0ff);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 30px rgba(11, 132, 243, 0.22);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 34px rgba(11, 132, 243, 0.28);
  }

  .error-note {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .error-visual {
    min-height: 100%;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(10, 97, 177, 0.05), rgba(10, 97, 177, 0.16)),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #dff0ff, #eef7ff);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .error-visual img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 22px 36px rgba(15, 48, 85, 0.18));
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .error-shell {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .error-copy {
      padding: 40px 24px 18px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .error-copy p {
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .error-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .error-visual {
      padding-top: 8px;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="error-shell">
    <section class="error-copy">
      <div class="error-badge">Error 404</div>
      <h1>La pagina que buscas no esta disponible.</h1>
      <p>
        La ruta solicitada no existe, fue movida o ya no se encuentra activa.
        Puedes volver al inicio del panel y continuar desde ahi.
      </p>
      <div class="error-actions">
        <a class="btn-primary" href="/app/default/#/inicio">Ir al inicio</a>
        <span class="error-note">Verifica la URL si esperabas otro contenido.</span>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="error-visual">
      <img src="https://s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/images-algmovi/logos/default.png" alt="Ilustracion de error 404">
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
